      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DOONGALLA ROCKET (6) jumped wide and had a clear run last start, leading all the way to score (25.51) at Warrnambool in a Grade 5 over 450m. Ran one of the fastest times on the program in his latest win. Has hit winning form and can go on with it. PYRENEES ACE (3) stalked the lead from a middle draw and boxed on well to finish 4 lengths back in third (23.24) at this track in a Mix 3/4 over 410m. Got the money at his only try from this box. Will give a great sight again. PAW PALMER (7) is worth forgiving for his last effort when fifth (26.01) at Warrnambool over 450m. Has never missed the frame here at the trip from four starts. Key runner on best form. PAW VORTEX (1) was out of placings last time (23.57) at this track in a Mix 3/4, finishing eighth and beaten 8 lengths. Has three wins already from this draw.",
